Given the following program and the first line of a loop, optimize it out via loop unrolling.. The program is struct c {
  int d : 18;
  int f;
};
struct c i;
int j;
int main() {
  struct c l = {24, 6738};
  l.d = j;
  int n = j && l.d;
  i.d = l.d | -(l.f && l.d) - n;
}
.                 The target to be optimized is `for (xxx) {`.
